# Privacy Policy

**Last Updated: June 2026**

## 1. Introduction

CipherCrack ("we", "our", or "us") is a mobile puzzle game designed to work completely offline. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.

## 2. Information We Do Not Collect

We do not collect any personal or non-personal information from users. This includes:

* No names, email addresses, or phone numbers
* No location data
* No device identifiers
* No analytics or usage tracking

## 3. Local Data Storage

The app may store limited data locally on your device, such as:

* Game progress
* High scores

This data is stored only on your device and is never shared with any third party.

## 4. Permissions

CipherCrack does not request any device permissions and does not access:

* Internet
* Storage
* Contacts
* Camera or microphone

## 5. Data Sharing

We do not share, sell, rent, or disclose any user data to third parties.

## 6. Third-Party Services

This app does not use any third-party services such as analytics or advertising networks.

## 7. Children's Privacy

CipherCrack is safe for all ages and does not collect any data from children or users.

## 8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page.

